{"tid":1917862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【印度偏方】議員稱牛尿牛糞可消毒預防武漢肺炎　印度男親身示範牛糞沐浴","createTime":"2020-03-09T17:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T03:00:20.000Z","uid":28114,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"80525c12972b3f39cee8a3ec59561c35550177c1","tid":1917862,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2580000/2584843/cow_thumb_20200309_E_V2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2580000%2F2584843%2Fcow_thumb_20200309_E_V2_600.jpg&h=349a398e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 印度男親身示範牛糞沐浴。<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情蔓延全球，世界各地均傳出多種偏方預防病毒。近日，有印度議員公開表示，牛尿、牛糞可以有助治療冠狀病毒，後來有印度男子亦親身以牛糞沐浴，聲稱牛糞是靈丹妙藥，可潔淨全身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2580000/2584843/3_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2580000%2F2584843%2F3_600.png&h=2d73c9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2人準備浸入牛糞池。(影片截圖)<br />\n<br />\n近日，網上瘋傳一條印度男子以牛糞沐浴的影片，震驚無數網民。影片中，2名男子站在牛糞池中，表示牛糞是靈丹妙藥，如果我們每6個月用牛糞洗一次澡，就可以潔淨全身。<br />\n<br />\n接著，2人便先後全身浸進牛糞池中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v3Fwhc8RcsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv3Fwhc8RcsA&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=fe45366e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v3Fwhc8RcsA</a><br />\n<br />\n此前，據印度媒體報道，印度人民黨議員Suman Haripriya曾在集合上表示，牛尿、牛糞可以有助治療冠狀病毒，甚至癌症。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，大家都知道牛糞非常有用。如果噴灑牛尿，就可以淨化一個區域。相信牛糞牛尿可以治療到冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n除了Suman Haripriya，另一名人民黨議員Sanjay Gupta也稱，古印度教儀式及牛尿可殺死空氣中及體內的病毒。另外，用牛糞清掃地板也可遏制病毒。<br />\n<br />\n古老的印度人都會用牛糞清掃地板，已證實這是種消毒劑，只不過現今的人類忘記了。我肯定如果大家再次這樣做，病毒就不會入侵他們的家。另外，大家也應該飲牛尿來預防病毒，因為母牛（Gau Mata）的產物都有神奇抗病毒的特性。<br />\n牛在印度被視為神聖的動物，當地文化中，用牛尿在治療用途已有悠久歷史。傳統上，牛糞可用於印度教的宗教儀式、藥物、肥料及燃料。<br />\n<br />\n截至3月9日0時，印度有34宗確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2584843/?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2584843%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d851a67c\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2584843/?r=mcsdfb</a>"},{"pid":"fd471d235cd502ef5bd1ff48d3a56b37aef49b40","tid":1917862,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:40:19.000Z","msg":"屌你正呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12d6c7847c2aab47491b6b7902e3843c4f3b7e7","tid":1917862,"uid":162268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:40:33.000Z","msg":"達爾文.jpg"},{"pid":"cb7f981e657be336746db77db43c2df6e745b7c7","tid":1917862,"uid":201414,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:44:25.000Z","msg":"唔出奇 留名等睇支那傳出食人可以對抗武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"e9974425f965f5baa40c1c6590009109c0682e0d","tid":1917862,"uid":248131,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:57:22.000Z","msg":"右邊條友係咪已經喺入面昏迷咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d618682100cf71289582eb01cab031f0dc624b","tid":1917862,"uid":105924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:58:18.000Z","msg":"隔住個MON都聞到陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facf18e2c83c35daf5cc223dd80ed22baaaf4389","tid":1917862,"uid":335063,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T17:59:29.000Z","msg":"其實錯唔曬 當你周身屎 邊個會接近你"},{"pid":"dbb037df8e457f2cf6abfe4c1c3e2aace189a7b1","tid":1917862,"uid":28114,"like":0,